                    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--chrome-dark); margin-bottom: 12px; line-height: 1.4;">
                        Tap slots to capture photos. Recommended: Front, Rear, Left, Right, Interior, Damage, Engine Bay, VIN Plate
                    </p>
